name: 001 Who's taking care of those boys that just want a call when your ovarian cysts pop?
description: In a memory of myself without illness, I only existed where my body was. At some point I took up at least 80% of the room-------the way I know chronic pain, my uterus and vagina are the only thing that I think about. That’s also why I’m a huge whore 😕 I’m not a very sought out sex worker because of my pain. Every like 5th offer “Bas” will want to buy a video off me, I have to keep reminding him I exist and he thinks I’m sexy. I feel like - whenever a group of people are making a fire I’m always the person standing around with twigs in my hands for too long because no one will take them from me.
